asukotelin/shirotelin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">shirotelin</a>, it is perfect! I don't feel blind anymore!</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1427 423' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-a992b86aba3c22b5a0f2cee2bee8b3ca'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-a992b86aba3c22b5a0f2cee2bee8b3ca)' width='1427' height='423' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAATCAYAAAAgcwuHAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAFIUlEQVR4nNVXiW7jOAzN/3/eLjCdXkns2PF935Yd7nt03LppBwvMdnY6AghRFEVLFPko77KwkOg%2bkvgUyDAMYuZRzGRkAhkzKk3T%2bMKv45W281v5K5l36z%2b0s7ExjqPu5VcTv7Nrmk6ypJQ26WSsjAyFkbboJcs6qZtZum6WqpqkbSbp%2b1ka9AV0SJRX9SQ1qG3nRV4uMp2DvTSrITM6T6Iu7dAu5eWVuEZtl3TEJGu7XORNux3/17arqkbSOJfO72RIRun9QWq/kTBqJEln3ViaG8nphP4iSWYkgl4Uj5KmIw49LTzl1z5JwUfkqVNIEMLJ%2beKwNJv0wHRUEI4SJ0ZlGYjrXK/H7YyfdLx/99aubXuxbF8COCFKMjmdPXG8QIIgkpN7luiQSGmVkj5kku5zya1CKquW%2bDkV%2bxTL/lBKHHfgGznalThuDZ49xlYF262EIR1WoI8gcyTPCznjG2VZ4tCpnM%2b%2bUhwn4roenJfK897Wfn84iXsOxPdj8YNYDkcXNs/KZ1mp8/bJg70QNkI5wH7i5BI/ZmKdMqwd9CIct8N8D91r73Qq3w2DEc9vcdhW4hSHwYYOtoPbieXkeHLcO%2bI5oQRuJC4c5die5HAWe370eX%2bGsxI9oA0csSA/HM6SJIX2R8vTsL1cZsUD5p7Iws/zhDw0SIkBNF75JQW6rtfx0i9z7Km7jIkX03XtcMWNZX4aJzEd9SfIZuDLRXsS02/ljbkAA9pOiqSSPoERhGYXAiBwY1lYIQ0GDVUS04DkYz5B6C9hPiBFZugtKZEwnCFnuDMFNA1UdxQPoZ1DTh3P71Unjhnu5pPC/eeagmARVZr3TdRK7TVKZVJLXgwKZG07gTcKWgybsjIqV6rNC5itsro2emiuIegRR2LgBkFu1adelsPZ4%2bKAC8Lkd9COFaAJWil95Pc5k8LPpIrL//UWftfh1QFxlEsFwBrqQZoUJQtOaFJEQVzBGbnKfmaT83wrkw1dXvqtE67MO%2be8mf%2bBA7d73My82cO7b6HtkiSXNuplHmcZ6x7vgVqmbpSuaKXLGunRf0ajQ1anbDdxK3t10EWmef7wgLe02tkecLW1bVv9lwgoigq1N5CnZxslxJXHvaVl52i7WlK%2bfX/WsnOHnjosT9/vD1ohvt09Q77XkmQD/e8wfng4ysOjpfqOG0DnSfXCMFE64hsnlC06XteBj1F%2bOceyd3%2b/x/ojMCQH3hQ677g%2bgDPSqhNgzeOThS